  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I managed to get kicked off, but unfortunately held on with one hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here I'm dangling on the street car when they decided-- a woman-- now talk about German mentality-- decided to bite my hand so I would let go and fall on the street.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Fortunately I didn't get that hurt-- hurt badly, but the incident was enough never, ever to even attempt to use anything that could possibly once again create such an incident-- for your own safety.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And nobody would ever know some of the things, the brutality.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One of the things that was also an incident that I walked in the street once, and obviously with my star, and you tried to avoid encountering any group of two or three or more youngsters.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] here are these blonde, blue-eyed uniformed Hitler Youth which somehow must have detected me, pursued me, and the one thing they wanted to see is what a circumcised penis looked like.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they dragged me out and ripped my clothes off and thought that that was very funny.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think it had a traumatic effect on me, but it's certainly-- you can't erase these memories of an example of what some people can do to you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not only get away with it, but be considered little big shot heroes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Past 1939, with the daily and nightly air raids-- at least in Cologne-- things were now getting terribly devastated because buildings were damaged.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that mean-- that meant fewer residences were available.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now was the time to hopefully get Jews out and have some Gentile occupying your residence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, most of the businesses had been already taken over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jewish businesses didn't exist in '39 and thereafter.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
